^c27STORY
^c00
After you returned home from your last mission, you enjoyed a moment of peace. You've been thinking about all your battles until now, and how the things could have been different.
Some days later, your commander sent you with a small group of soldiers to the now abandoned castle from where you found the SOD with the mission of locate a few missing members of your army.
^PAGE 5
^c27STORY
^c00
Searching inside the castle, you realized that your friends were no longer alive: they got turned into the fat freaks you have met before. There was no way of nazis could have acquired the spear once more. No one and nothing could. Without answers, you returned to your HQ to inform your commander.
^PAGE 6
^c27STORY
^c00
To avoid more trouble with that castle, your army has bombed the entire installation, eliminating any experiments, researches and weapons.
A week after that, Allies discovered that nazi troops found an old temple in north of Europe. There they have constructed their HQ while you was on your last mission. More trouble for B.J. A small group of nazi scientists survived your encounter and has continued the abomination process.
^PAGE 7
^c27STORY
^c00
Unfortunately, their experiments has let them make their army huger by using some unknown tool of great energy. It, somehow, allowed nazi to control the demonic creatures. Even worst, they used one of the teleport artfacts created by the SOD in order to get access directly to hell. Now more evil monsters will battle against you.
^PAGE 8
^c27STORY
^c00
To Allies, there was no possibility of nazis get able to battle once more. It is unknown what kind of creatures are there, who is commanding this operation and which is this energy tool. Your mission will be find your way to the temple by crossing the nazi installation, eliminate their leader and find this object. Good luck.
