^c27INTERACTIVE OBJECTS
^c00
There are 3 interactive objects: the landmine, the destructable pillar and the explodable drum. Landmines are found in outside areas in the green grass camps. Those pillars can be found everywhere, reavealing extra passages or secrets. The explodable druns can kill your enemies as well as kill you. Watch out in what are you shooting.
^PAGE 27
^c28LEVELS
^c00
This addon contains 14 regular levels, 4 boss levels and 3 secret ones. It have 3 different scenarios: the outside levels, the castle and the temple. Some of the levels may have special tasks to complete them, without the use of the ordinary elevator switch. Those tasks will be presented before the level starts. In harder difficulties, health items will raise a bit more of health, to keep the game more enjoyable.
^PAGE 28
^c28SECRET LEVELS
^c00
There is one secret level for each type of scenario. They takes as base the original levels from Wolf3D (with some modifications). They are all timed levels to make you a new challenge.
